name: Magical Girl Friendship Squad: Origins
overview: When a little red panda named Nut arrives in the apartment of two directionless 20-somethings and gives them the magical abilities to transform into superheroes, Alex and Daisy are forced to get their lives together to save the universe. With the help of their magical objects, Alex and Daisy learn to fight off interdimensional bounty hunters and protect their mysterious panda friend who claims to be the creator of the universe.
